<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/adam-land> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Adam Land was appointed Senior Director of the Office for the Internal Market and the Subsidy Advice Unit on 1 July 2024. Before being appointed to this role, Adam was Senior Director of Remedies, Business and Financial Analysis at the CMA and has previously worked in a variety of roles in competition policy and HM Treasury. Adam chairs the Health and Wellbeing Senior Steering Group for the UK Civil Service."@en .
